<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(229, 51, 51);"><strong>划算金</strong></span><span style="line-height: 23.9999980926514px;">：</span>下单价减去划算价的<strong>返利金额</strong>。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">例如：下单价119元 - 划算价55.93=划算金63.07元</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><strong>下单价：</strong>是指买家到指定交易平台提交订单后实际付款的总额，即到指定店铺购买的实付价格。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><strong>划算价：</strong>该价格为买家购买商品的优惠价格，即优惠价，只有在平台平台抢购才能享受。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><strong>返还划算金：&nbsp;</strong>即划算金，下单价减去划算价返利的金额。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><strong>折扣：</strong>是指到卖家店铺购的买价格优惠比例，公式：折扣=（划算价&divide;下单价）&times;100%。</span></p>
